<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">機緣</cb:mulu>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B494.0592c" n="0592c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="16"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="16"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="16"><cb:jhead>雨山和尚語錄卷第十六</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c02"/><byline cb:type="editor">嗣法門人　　編</byline>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">頌古</cb:mulu><head>頌古</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">世尊拈花</cb:mulu><head>世尊拈花</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c05"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0592c0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">拈花謾道傳心法。誰信分明是禍胎。胡種不教除滅
<lb ed="J" n="0592c06"/>盡。太平風月幾時來。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">文殊仗劍</cb:mulu><head>文殊仗劍</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c08"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0592c0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">怪底文殊達眾情。莫邪持逼甚分明。縱然蕩得煙塵
<lb ed="J" n="0592c09"/>盡。又有痴頑戀太平。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">六祖風幡</cb:mulu><head>六祖風幡</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c11"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0592c1101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">不是風幡復是誰。老盧特煞露全機。直饒透過威音
<lb ed="J" n="0592c12"/>去。那免通身帶水泥。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c13"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">不二法門</cb:mulu><head>不二法門</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c14"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0592c1401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">不二門中。語說默說。文殊維摩。各得一橛。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">馬師鹽醬</cb:mulu><head>馬師鹽醬</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c16"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0592c1601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">馬祖當年用意賒。傷鹽傷醬稱當家。兒孫引得猶多
<lb ed="J" n="0592c17"/>事。到處逢人只撒沙。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">歸宗一味</cb:mulu><head>歸宗一味</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c19"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0592c1901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">踏翻大海未為險。踢倒須彌始是奇。直透長安無別
<lb ed="J" n="0592c20"/>道。行人不用泣多岐。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c21"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">婆子燒庵</cb:mulu><head>婆子燒庵</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c22"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0592c2201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">道得分明事轉非。老婆不重嫁時衣。投機若也知親
<lb ed="J" n="0592c23"/>切。須是人間大闡提。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c24"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">趙州勘婆</cb:mulu><head>趙州勘婆</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c25"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0592c2501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">紅爐焰裏橫身易。荊棘叢中出手難。冷眼看來成笑
<lb ed="J" n="0592c26"/>具。幾人不被道途瞞。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c27"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">長沙玩月</cb:mulu><head>長沙玩月</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c28"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0592c2801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">言中有響全機出。直下乘風用不虧。縱使大千俱踏
<lb ed="J" n="0592c29"/>倒。大虫猶自落便宜。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0592c30"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">九峰首座</cb:mulu><head>九峰首座</head>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B494.0593a" n="0593a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a01"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">雪覆蘆花古岸邊。客鄉何苦尚留連。要知咫尺家山
<lb ed="J" n="0593a02"/>路。踏破珊瑚海底天。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">南泉活計</cb:mulu><head>南泉活計</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a04"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">南泉活計。兒孫得玅。不許夜行。投明須到。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">曹山驢井</cb:mulu><head>曹山驢井</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a06"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">海月騰輝。珊瑚聳秀。覿露新條。天高地厚。婆娑影轉
<lb ed="J" n="0593a07"/>不停機。黃頭碧眼應難搆。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">雪峰鱉鼻</cb:mulu><head>雪峰鱉鼻</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a09"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">旌旗纔動五雲開。鬼面神頭轉出來。把盞靈前三鬯
<lb ed="J" n="0593a10"/>酒。大家拍手舞高臺。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">烏臼二僧</cb:mulu><head>烏臼二僧</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a12"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">掌握洪機。文經武緯。把定乾坤。英雄喪氣。烏臼老。真
<lb ed="J" n="0593a13"/>可畏。只有受璧之心。全無割城之意。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">孚上座悟道</cb:mulu><head>孚上座悟道</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a15"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593a1501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">遶徑尋花逐日來。桃源洞口應時開。循環看遍春歸
<lb ed="J" n="0593a16"/>去。始識靈苗不受栽。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">黃檗酒糟</cb:mulu><head>黃檗酒糟</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a18"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593a1801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">昨夜滿山風雨打。草庵卸卻琉璃瓦。大唐國內手親
<lb ed="J" n="0593a19"/>垂。直下送君歸去也。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a20"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">長沙崔顥</cb:mulu><head>長沙崔顥</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a21"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593a2101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">百千諸佛問何之。落處分明一首詩。長憶杜陵曾有
<lb ed="J" n="0593a22"/>語。風流儒雅亦吾師。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a23"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">心不是佛</cb:mulu><head>心不是佛</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a24"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593a2401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">古殿分明長綠苔。那來位次得安排。紛紛門外閒遊
<lb ed="J" n="0593a25"/>者。徒<anchor xml:id="beg_e5" type="cb-app"/>羨<anchor xml:id="end_e5"/>當時作賦才。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a26"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">三頓痛棒</cb:mulu><head>三頓痛棒</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a27"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593a2701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">細姑曉起覓紅籹。欲展奩籠恐事長。直把金針相度
<lb ed="J" n="0593a28"/>與。從教出手繡鴦鴛。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a29"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">巖頭一橈</cb:mulu><head>巖頭一橈</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593a30"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593a3001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">抱得阿嬌覿面呈。鄂陽渡子一橈行。自從喪卻渾家
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B494.0593b" n="0593b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b01"/>後。門外春來草漫生。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">南泉如如</cb:mulu><head>南泉如如</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b03"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593b0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">掣開金鎖。闖入異類。但念水草。餘無所會。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">趙州菴主</cb:mulu><head>趙州菴主</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b05"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593b0501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">白雲深處不藏身。轉過鄰西再問人。報道昨宵蘆管
<lb ed="J" n="0593b06"/>動。暗中贏得武林春。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">臨濟栽松</cb:mulu><head>臨濟栽松</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b08"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593b0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">蒿枝拂後更無私。鳥道行來敵霸師。抹過雲橫三座
<lb ed="J" n="0593b09"/>棧。望風只見豎降旗。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">狗無佛性</cb:mulu><head>狗無佛性</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b11"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593b1101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">起屍虎非德。歃血貓未功。爭似渠一齒。下下不曾空。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">龐公指雪</cb:mulu><head>龐公指雪</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b13"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593b1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">六花指問全禪客。嶮崖之機直下闢。自非解衝逆浪
<lb ed="J" n="0593b14"/>波。那免龍門遭點額。襄陽翁。襄陽翁。電光影裏捕飛
<lb ed="J" n="0593b15"/>龍。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">南陽無情</cb:mulu><head>南陽無情</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b17"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593b1701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">垂老猶然不歇心。慣針枯木作龍吟。分明妙唱無私
<lb ed="J" n="0593b18"/>曲。幾箇能聆格外音。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b19"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">睦州轉藏</cb:mulu><head>睦州轉藏</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b20"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593b2001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">纍纍龍文盈海藏。睦州轉得何通暢。勸君不用苦鑽
<lb ed="J" n="0593b21"/>研。本事伽陀空色相。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b22"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">百丈再參</cb:mulu><head>百丈再參</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b23"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593b2301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">豎拂掛拂。野狐戀窟。即此離此。鉤頭有餌。忽然迸出
<lb ed="J" n="0593b24"/>迅雷聲。須彌岌峇海波騰。丈老耳聾重落草。回頭失
<lb ed="J" n="0593b25"/>卻來時道。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b26"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">非心非佛</cb:mulu><head>非心非佛</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b27"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593b2701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">蘆花拂拂晚風輕。罷釣歸來月正明。不脫煙蓑橫石
<lb ed="J" n="0593b28"/>枕。子陵從此謝閒名。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b29"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">六祖不會</cb:mulu><head>六祖不會</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593b30"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593b3001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">行者分明不識丁。獦獠何得繼傳燈。只憑者句無私
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B494.0593c" n="0593c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c01"/>語。壓倒黃梅七百僧。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">雪峰烏石</cb:mulu><head>雪峰烏石</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c03"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593c0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">軍旅相逢要合符。攔胸把住不虛圖。老觀展出威音
<lb ed="J" n="0593c04"/><anchor xml:id="beg_e6" type="cb-app"/>券<anchor xml:id="end_e6"/>。笑倒庵前箇野狐。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">嚴陽一物</cb:mulu><head>嚴陽一物</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c06"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593c0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">鸞鏡初開照影偏。憐君多在未生前。白雲乍可來青
<lb ed="J" n="0593c07"/>嶂。明月難教下碧天。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">佛鑒悟由</cb:mulu><head>佛鑒悟由</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c09"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593c0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">昨夜羅睺星入宮。官差民擾不從容。還家幸遇君平
<lb ed="J" n="0593c10"/>卜。一爆龜紋兆吉凶。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">南泉斬貓</cb:mulu><head>南泉斬貓</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c12"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593c1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">國有憲章人自律。家無白澤鬼成精。南泉握起青鋒
<lb ed="J" n="0593c13"/>劍。報盡人間兩不平。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">章敬草鞋</cb:mulu><head>章敬草鞋</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c15"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593c1501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">草鞋拂卻利如兵。撲落金塵秪一聲。花雨不來巖自
<lb ed="J" n="0593c16"/>寂。水雲何處覓空生。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">靈雲桃花</cb:mulu><head>靈雲桃花</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c18"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593c1801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">桃花歲歲滿山蹊。怪煞靈雲不當意。昨日偶然一舉
<lb ed="J" n="0593c19"/>頭。曼殊肝腦皆塗地。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c20"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">玄沙未徹</cb:mulu><head>玄沙未徹</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c21"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593c2101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">妙峰孤頂獨尊渠。神臂弓開力有餘。一鏃遼天飛過
<lb ed="J" n="0593c22"/>後。那知不在草庵居。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c23"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">俱胝一指</cb:mulu><head>俱胝一指</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c24"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593c2401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">孟嘗席上列千奇。咽得全牛便不饑。堪笑幾多珠履
<lb ed="J" n="0593c25"/>客。酩然錯認口頭肥。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c26"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">德山挾複</cb:mulu><head>德山挾複</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c27"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593c2701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">三戌漁陽再渡遼。騂弓在臂劍橫腰。蠻王自有過人
<lb ed="J" n="0593c28"/>策。莫傍陰山來射鵰。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c29"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">密師白兔</cb:mulu><head>密師白兔</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0593c30"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0593c3001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">龍樓幔合全休致。體臥清風豈有私。頭上寶花如不
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B494.0594a" n="0594a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a01"/>卸。還應拱立下丹墀。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">夾山境話</cb:mulu><head>夾山境話</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a03"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">古路層層苔蘚封。松杉日老鶴巢空。翻身木馬衝雲
<lb ed="J" n="0594a04"/>去。夜半嘶開嶺上風。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">投子大死</cb:mulu><head>投子大死</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a06"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">朽榦多年化作龍。爪牙雖備用無功。睡中觸發冰河
<lb ed="J" n="0594a07"/>燄。燒得新羅滿國紅。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">龍牙羅睺</cb:mulu><head>龍牙羅睺</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a09"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">流水高山志不衰。一聲長響出奇材。當時不遇中郎
<lb ed="J" n="0594a10"/>鑑。絕代絲桐幾作灰。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">迦葉剎竿</cb:mulu><head>迦葉剎竿</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a12"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">分明一帶官唐路。慶喜行來特地難。不是剎竿門外
<lb ed="J" n="0594a13"/>倒。何時夢得到長安。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">文殊白椎</cb:mulu><head>文殊白椎</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a15"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594a1501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">谷口雲收化日低。春光喜見十分肥。東風何事不相
<lb ed="J" n="0594a16"/>惜。吹落殘紅遍馬啼。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">馬師玩月</cb:mulu><head>馬師玩月</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a18"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594a1801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">寶月凝虛。光生銀海。作者競酬。圓轉無礙。經入藏兮
<lb ed="J" n="0594a19"/>箭直鋒。禪歸海兮函得蓋。王老師。獨超邁。笑倒明州
<lb ed="J" n="0594a20"/>憨布袋。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a21"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">馬祖不安</cb:mulu><head>馬祖不安</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a22"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594a2201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">日面佛。月面佛。馬師特煞露風骨。爭如埋向暗窗前。
<lb ed="J" n="0594a23"/>免得人爭第二月。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a24"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">女子出定</cb:mulu><head>女子出定</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a25"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594a2501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">三箇孩兒合箇娘。一棚傀儡弄當場。牽來拽去資人
<lb ed="J" n="0594a26"/>笑。贏得風流滿大唐。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a27"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">賓主歷然</cb:mulu><head>賓主歷然</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a28"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594a2801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">五月天申好令辰。一雙艾虎踞當門。更加兩道陰符
<lb ed="J" n="0594a29"/>敕。百怪千妖盡喪魂。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594a30"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">臨濟破夏</cb:mulu><head>臨濟破夏</head>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B494.0594b" n="0594b"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b01"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594b0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">尋常海上跨神鰲。平地如何轉喫交。縱使趁回開血
<lb ed="J" n="0594b02"/>掌。鞋跟<anchor xml:id="beg_e7" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_e7"/>是落蓬蒿。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">馬師四句</cb:mulu><head>馬師四句</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b04"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594b0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">馬師父子家聲重。心手都盧無別共。不影金鎚暗裏
<lb ed="J" n="0594b05"/>拋。者僧那覺頂門痛。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">三喚侍者</cb:mulu><head>三喚侍者</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b07"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594b0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">國師三喚莫相猜。樓閣分明八字開。長恨春歸無覓
<lb ed="J" n="0594b08"/>處。不知轉入此中來。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">高峰真贊</cb:mulu><head>高峰真贊</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b10"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594b1001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">十載勞勞苦問津。浣花溪上始逢人。相將惟戀風光
<lb ed="J" n="0594b11"/>好。那識桃源別有春。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">高峰枕子</cb:mulu><head>高峰枕子</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b13"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594b1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">十丈珊瑚一擊開。到頭不<anchor xml:id="beg_e8" type="cb-app"/>羨<anchor xml:id="end_e8"/>季倫財。怎如直入蓬蒿
<lb ed="J" n="0594b14"/>去。百二山河眼底灰。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b15"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">子湖狗子</cb:mulu><head>子湖狗子</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b16"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594b1601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">驀地逢人便展威。爪牙真箇利如錐。任他攫霧拏雲
<lb ed="J" n="0594b17"/>者。到此應教點額回。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b18"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">龍潭紙燈</cb:mulu><head>龍潭紙燈</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b19"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594b1901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">卸卻紅籹洗盡香。冰心一片付仙郎。鶯聲喚醒生前
<lb ed="J" n="0594b20"/>夢。花落幽巖月上窗。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b21"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殃崛產難</cb:mulu><head>殃崛產難</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b22"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594b2201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">瞿曇掣轉靈符。殃崛踏翻毒箭。驀地激電光飛。鬼面
<lb ed="J" n="0594b23"/>神頭俱現。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b24"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">柏樹子話</cb:mulu><head>柏樹子話</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b25"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594b2501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">銀漢風高著眼難。月華影射暮江寒。堪嗟多少浪遊
<lb ed="J" n="0594b26"/>者。錯把山河當玉看。</l></lg>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b27"/><p cb:type="head3" xml:id="pJ40p0594b2701">又</p>
<lb ed="J" n="0594b28"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594b2801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">少室神機。宣符奪命。匝地鋒馳。急如律令。煙塵鼓蕩
<lb ed="J" n="0594b29"/>兮草木成兵。象龍蹴踏兮森羅遭印。五眼難窺。二聞
<lb ed="J" n="0594b30"/>絕聽。咄。昨夜銀河垂斗柄。</l></lg></cb:div>
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B494.0594c" n="0594c"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">最初父母</cb:mulu><head>最初父母</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c02"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594c0201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">九烏盡。乾坤黑。莓苔結滿空王宅。五子奉重且無門。
<lb ed="J" n="0594c03"/>帝釋雨花成狼籍。君不見。曇摩昔日至梁邦。對聖分
<lb ed="J" n="0594c04"/>明云不識。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">虎在深山</cb:mulu><head>虎在深山</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c06"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594c0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">紅日逗。珠林秀。鸞鶴機停成過咎。怎如奮翮直沖霄。
<lb ed="J" n="0594c07"/>縈身金網應時透。歸去來。明月瘦。故山風景還依舊。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">虛空背面</cb:mulu><head>虛空背面</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c09"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594c0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">洪荒闢。天機洩。冰花簇簇紅爐結。璇璣不動運無私。
<lb ed="J" n="0594c10"/>鳥道揮來千仞鐵。神鋒別河山。盡染屠空血。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">楚王城畔</cb:mulu><head>楚王城畔</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c12"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594c1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">席卷長河一滴投。當家須信出風流。楚王城畔朝宗
<lb ed="J" n="0594c13"/>客。錯過蟾蜍月上秋。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">牛過窗櫺</cb:mulu><head>牛過窗櫺</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c15"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594c1501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">異草靈苗曾不顧。還家豈踏今時路。尾巴尖上老婆
<lb ed="J" n="0594c16"/>禪。徒把虛空重指注。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">雲門聞聲</cb:mulu><head>雲門聞聲</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c18"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594c1801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">入得觀音妙理門。看來猶自墮深坑。怎如透出韶陽
<lb ed="J" n="0594c19"/>普。踢倒須彌撒手行。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c20"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">寶壽開堂</cb:mulu><head>寶壽開堂</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c21"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594c2101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">勢若崩雷迸得來。定乾坤眼棒頭開。鎮州人且由他
<lb ed="J" n="0594c22"/>瞎。自有<anchor xml:id="beg_e9" type="cb-app"/>佳<anchor xml:id="end_e9"/>聲遍九垓。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c23"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">臨濟真人</cb:mulu><head>臨濟真人</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c24"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594c2401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">白拈手段最稱奇。把得明珠暗裏施。擬欲窺光雲萬
<lb ed="J" n="0594c25"/>里。卷舒曾不落今時。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c26"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">清淨本然</cb:mulu><head>清淨本然</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c27"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594c2701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">野老門前化日幽。垂衣致治有嘉猷。封疆秪欲分夷
<lb ed="J" n="0594c28"/>夏。頓起干戈百草頭。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c29"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">有句無句</cb:mulu><head>有句無句</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0594c30"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0594c3001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">解轉機輪要絕功。乘言早見嶽摩空。最憐兩處同風
<pb ed="J" xml:id="J40.B494.0595a" n="0595a"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a01"/>事。雖發千鈞不露銘。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">麻谷觀音</cb:mulu><head>麻谷觀音</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a03"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0595a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">觀音面面隨機現。互換臨時展大悲。兩箇白拈伎倆
<lb ed="J" n="0595a04"/>絕。到頭誰是落便宜。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">世尊初生</cb:mulu><head>世尊初生</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a06"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0595a0601" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">割據既然非善策。征誅亦不是良圖。要為祖域開新
<lb ed="J" n="0595a07"/>運。垂拱還他大丈夫。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a08"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">未離兜率</cb:mulu><head>未離兜率</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a09"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0595a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">未離兜率。<anchor xml:id="beg_ea" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_ea"/>降王宮。剎那見得。猶未通宗。瞿曇老。重
<lb ed="J" n="0595a10"/>入草。十年歸不得。忘卻來時道。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a11"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">世尊明星</cb:mulu><head>世尊明星</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a12"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0595a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">玉殿瓊樓不肯居。卻來雪嶺甘受餓。縱饒說得悟明
<lb ed="J" n="0595a13"/>星。難免兒孫平地坐。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a14"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">武帝達磨</cb:mulu><head>武帝達磨</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a15"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0595a1501" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">一敲敲出鳳凰髓。一擊擊碎明月珠。老胡伎倆無多
<lb ed="J" n="0595a16"/>子。天上人間識也無。</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">龐公指雪</cb:mulu><head>龐公指雪</head>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a18"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0595a1801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">的的分明是六花。要將落處驗龍蛇。全公只解隨人
<lb ed="J" n="0595a19"/>轉。縱有神通未足誇。</l></lg>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a20"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0595a2001" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">臨別輕輕露一籌。直中誰信曲如鉤。當時若縱機先
<lb ed="J" n="0595a21"/>術。管保龐公血掌收。</l></lg>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a22"/><lg xml:id="lgJ40p0595a2201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">妙展機鋒是老龐。只憑豪氣壓諸方。馬<unclear></unclear>腳下多神
<lb ed="J" n="0595a23"/>駿。蹴踏居然小八荒。</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a24"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a25"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a26"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a27"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a28"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a29"/>
<lb ed="J" n="0595a30"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="16"><cb:jhead>雨山和尚語錄卷第十六<note place="inline">終</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
